Subject: [PATCH] Configure script

Add configure script that exports some environment variables to
configure the build and run qmake with the appropriate prefix.
---
 configure |    4 ++++
 1 file changed, 4 insertions(+)
 create mode 100755 configure

diff --git a/configure b/configure
new file mode 100755
index 0000000..1a93e6e
--- /dev/null
+++ b/configure
@@ -0,0 +1,4 @@
+#!/bin/sh
+export USE_WEBGL=true
+export NO_X11="true"
+qmake QUPZILLA_PREFIX=/usr/
